{"tid":1998986,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根據英國衛報報道，流血革命之苗頭早於去年八月已於香港抗爭運動中已經出現","createTime":"2020-05-02T22:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T22:41:17.000Z","uid":294955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc3087400791f88bc877a9d7a1197db81c5b357","tid":1998986,"uid":294955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6GRHvM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6GRHvM.png&h=a1991933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/aug/31/hong-kong-revolution-no-war-is-without-bloodshed-protesters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2019%2Faug%2F31%2Fhong-kong-revolution-no-war-is-without-bloodshed-protesters&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufSDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=402e55b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/aug/31/hong-kong-revolution-no-war-is-without-bloodshed-protesters</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xZDmgK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xZDmgK.png&h=a29fbd96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「<span style=\"color: gold;\">當警方濫用其權力而他們無須面對後果時，一場革命已擁有合理基礎了。我接受革命和流血。革命就是一種戰爭，戰爭沒有不涉暴力的・・・倘若我們的暴力可帶來積極正面的改變，我願意參與其中。</span>」<br />\n--- 27歲電腦工程師/抗爭者"},{"pid":"174b9eea568e0e5a8543f1195d255085a02994a7","tid":1998986,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d940f96ae4447b7e1b5a8eba201e40f7d185ba77","tid":1998986,"uid":356914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:12:57.000Z","msg":"無論過咗幾耐 仇一定會報 還眼 還命"},{"pid":"d170366b1da1e01b7759c1d59047f633229e89fd","tid":1998986,"uid":294955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T22:41:17.000Z","msg":"中共文宣不敢提<span style=\"color: gold;\">革命</span>一詞，我地就愈要大大聲聲講。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭運動中出現嘅並非<span style=\"color: blue;\">恐怖主義苗頭</span>，而係<span style=\"color: gold;\">流血革命</span>嘅苗頭。中共去年八月中以前者不實之指控抹黑抗爭者，其實係要轉移大眾嘅視線。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EhayWUA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEhayWUA.png&h=096b3b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於<span style=\"color: gold;\">革命</span>一詞暗示其行動包括流血含必要性同正當性，中共及港共一直不敢正面提及（一旦廿三條立法則另論）。<br />\n<br />\n我地必須指出，抗爭者<span style=\"color: gold;\">絕非</span>無差別襲擊平民(civilians, 見以下<span style=\"color: pink;\">恐怖主義</span>之英文定義)的恐怖主義者（<span style=\"color: teal;\">7.21白衣人先至係</span>）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQ4PvaR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQ4PvaR.png&h=5fae7032&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}